CONVERSION
----------------
Convert .jpegs to .avi          : ffmpeg -i im%3d.jpg video.avi
Convert .avi to .jpeg           : ffmpeg -i video.avi -f image2 im%03d.jpg
Convert mjpeg.avi to .jpegs     : ffmpeg -i video.avi -c:v copy -bsf:v mjpeg2jpeg im%d.jpg

Check if video is mjpeg         : ffprobe -v error -select_streams v:0 -show_entries stream=codec_name -of default=nw=1 input.avi


FLAGS
-----
Quality 2-31, lower is better   : -qscale:v $value
Set output resolution           : ffmpeg -i input.avi -s 720x480 -c:a copy output.avi
Set output resolution same a/r  : ffmpeg -i input.avi -s 720:-1 -c:a copy output.avi
Change frame-rate               : ffmpeg -i input.avi -filter:v fps=fps=30 output.avi


WATERMARK
---------
Put watermark on video          : ffmpeg -i $file -i image.png -filter_complex "overlay=15:H-h-50" -codec:a copy "output.avi"
  Center                        : "overlay=(W-w)/2:(H-h)/2"
  Top-left                      : "overlay=5:5"            
  Top-right                     : "overlay=W-w-5:5"        
  Bottom-left                   : "overlay=5:H-h-5"        
  Bottom-right                  : "overlay=W-w-5:H-h-5"    



